  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d4ca2fc3-9129-4c17-b756-0295db18a78d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f57d74cc-554f-42ab-ae7e-88bbac2239cc\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8fb7f5aa-165f-4b38-b7e6-b74af736f1be\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 9</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6f21b460-6ad8-4d74-bbb6-dde09d0115ad\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c3a14331-af40-4390-906a-b5f6b79c5269\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a51625fb-39cf-41ef-9820-41dd672be801\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1e09f1f3-ba1e-483f-8e46-88eca7217dbf\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[집중]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f5cb4718-df88-48e2-867c-dedea0e4a4a4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3750b622-aecf-45ea-b80b-bff07344b1e0\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>어제는 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-585e1781-5292-4c1a-a46d-7ba145c3ecc8\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 8</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-96a1ba49-fd9f-4bfa-9a1d-1ed15f632675\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>에서 메인페이지의 UI모습을 적었습니다. 실제 메인에서 템플릿을 선택한 후 주문단에서 이루어 지는 모습을 보여드리겠습니다. 다만 본작업은 실제 중간 스토리보드 보강작업 후 약간의 디자인 수정이나 스키마가 변경될 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6e31e449-4357-44db-aa77-acd5bfcb1321\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2f737b0b-461c-432b-b773-77834e9a798b\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b7c8ed73-f698-4456-be75-088ffa7bbac6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9d22c381-ffcb-4870-a5f9-90fa9163004e\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-168a1953-c637-41da-8001-336e3e8a773d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e23aa6e7-b414-495b-9203-8f0f685f6959\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-747e76ed-ebf4-4dd1-bc2e-b7c065a192c4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>STEP1. 메인페이지에서 만족하는 템플릿을 선택합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-26ff69ea-4a5b-4598-aa66-7b7e455b72d4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-60bd85d9-e58b-4ca0-b2d9-2b68fb382f82\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a9afa2d8-c6ad-429d-b6f8-8e0d4830d818\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 8</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8a113fd8-6c09-4b93-83ef-3be35d737c3e\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">의 예시에서 처럼 메인에서 자신에게 가장 적당하고 비슷한 템플릿을 선택하여 클릭합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1009f230-686e-4412-a790-9a8c0f93d1ad\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7bd8ef57-6d8c-4f55-ba75-e20b316b84e8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8c7d34c4-534c-4f93-8415-5c184ee69400\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>쿡더다자인은 좋은 템플릿으로 보다 많은 양질의 디자인을 제공하겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-36af2ea0-fd8d-4c29-b465-4c10e8ee8c19\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6315e510-d1a1-4e14-80e0-9fc6faeb1224\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-af77daa5-d0a0-482f-a615-cda366de1e68\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e870e244-a7db-4e6a-9db0-d5bc96811322\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-90cd2337-7a91-4eb9-b8df-2172c57bd5c4\" style=\"color:#ba0000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>선택한 유형 : 교원 A01</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-81a18cbb-a51b-4d0d-8e07-cf311d43ac05\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:349px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222888436979/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e73585ab-88d2-40f6-814b-b45ce6b0b912\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7f03ffcf-2755-4a3b-b131-4bede010fb5a\" style=\"\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 메인</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6f34e87-0427-4865-b698-ac04e112864b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-04a7d8e2-35cd-4c76-ad4e-429fee64f1c3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5d61ce39-3226-4206-be98-55b170d06c85\" style=\"\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b7d53961-9d61-4faf-93c4-0bb16946a4bd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f1f547c5-09c1-4a72-8c5b-e26f67f2e1a9\" style=\"\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-2476fad0-7f2f-4a63-be6c-ef9e3cc7760f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-44795d4d-de2c-4ca8-8709-2a322e9bf6ca\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-63be2f81-f48e-482d-b0a2-38e8a3be4347\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>STEP2. 주문을 접수하는 페이지로 이동됩니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ac680508-eabc-4f8a-ab27-db62e086ad4c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0d024451-e358-4c10-9585-8c669905602c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bb85f0c8-eb97-42c9-b812-c30a48c750ed\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">주문서 작성 페이지로 이동됩니다. 이 템플릿에서 나의 정보를 입력하고 노출되지 않은 가격을 요청하여 홈페이지를 통해 견적금액을 통보받아 입금 후 프로세스 진행을 통해 결제와 생산, 배송 그리고 구매완료까지의 프로세스로 진행됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-67fbec90-5367-456d-9c1a-f5f62a766a52\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:686px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222888436979/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c98643ef-c22c-499b-be57-1d52de1bde6a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-aebbd18d-27c2-42c2-8d35-c3c9c1ed38df\" style=\"\">주문서작성 및 견적서 요청</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3cc7728c-2cb4-4a29-9703-970ff331bcc8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08b5be8e-57a5-4e7d-951b-43c5b1019a23\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7386f583-c8ef-4039-9135-e9c6795dd7ed\" style=\"color:#777777;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f95d05d9-1b5b-4b83-8665-7a6819a53aa3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b426791f-3064-4cb3-a803-67e2552f2c46\" style=\"color:#777777;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-e895b607-7350-4d12-8100-cf03bc5507ed\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-63df6228-b510-483e-b2b3-78f88e0438d6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-10532e91-cd8c-4583-bf82-81566072f59e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>STEP3. 주문서를 통해 얻어내야 할 정보</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-37167e49-f348-47fe-83b3-d8da1d1f8efd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-de6fcfd3-b509-4b11-adeb-701bf4896045\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b5498ee2-9aa8-48c1-bafb-b15d85c7d014\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">주문서 작성을 통해 우리는 고객과 소통합니다. 템플릿으로 디자인을 유혹한다면 그 템플릿의 변형을 통해 디자인을 수정하고 커뮤니케이션하여 고객과 소통하는 프로세스를 만들어야 합니다. 이때 고객과의 소통을 위해 필요한 정보가 주문서에 담겨야 합니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4aed5727-b2e9-478a-b3ff-e32ee13befa5\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9911f112-38ce-468b-a6ce-cecb49f4c020\" style=\"color:#777777;\">​</span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4fa429c4-0fdd-4f56-8ea7-434c1a593df1\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2c2e10bf-7906-4282-ab1a-9118fb94a4bd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>주문사양</b></span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-de22fc93-e4c4-4b49-89b9-705b77f723da\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-daed13cb-64ff-4f92-b509-c1570e18f31b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5867fd53-1d7e-4fd6-9555-fc2f32b50153\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>- 종이종류</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b4357e71-ecf2-4424-936c-01f2b1715a2c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 고객이 변경할 수 있습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a00b9a1-ff84-4f73-8896-01eec4a3e936\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-831a327a-7f57-42d1-894b-aaa99989ed1f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-90bb295a-9e25-43c1-8cb0-189a0113921f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>- 사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7ca92448-7f36-4e17-9e90-cc5e26041104\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 사이즈는 템플릿 유형으로 정해져 있으므로 선택이 불가능합니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-abc0f2eb-2e98-4eb9-baa2-8ca6d18ab7a1\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8bc7099f-25ac-413c-8d59-62d321179088\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c6cf4873-99b5-4326-9fbb-e39fda586e1a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>- 인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c9522c52-f200-4270-92eb-5d3bec731d63\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 단면, 양면 또한 템플릿에 따라 달라집니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-445b4d22-e48b-4291-8d0f-44eb48c01e93\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ac1658bd-a1f1-4059-ae65-15d8a9e38505\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e7c057c3-3cab-4033-bc54-7225a46eae49\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>- 후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f5979085-2aca-408e-8aa5-58447983bedc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 후공정도 템플릿에 따라 다릅니다. 박인쇄나 라운드등의 후공정은 맞는 템플릿을 선택해야 합니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3453c4aa-550a-4447-8437-b154616ce31f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ddeb587a-f10c-4426-8b70-995c2be28777\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-293f7850-3e3b-407a-b9bd-37a9ee1624bb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>- 수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-16b8343e-470b-4544-99b1-2d96ff96413a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 고객이 변경할 수 있습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-527fffcd-c1f7-4ac9-9afa-b3a9afd4ce3e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9cf8e23e-a270-4c19-8b05-a0409afbaece\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd644dfe-7eda-4639-984f-7942120d8b9d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9d48c05b-b5f7-425b-98aa-9ddc3b05063a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>2. 주문 내용정보</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a0a17e82-99f9-4145-8f58-33d261348b75\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a2f5b67a-e9f5-415c-a6a9-d2e955a78e9e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-07c41a5c-c2c1-4720-9dd5-4f2b4323c8d8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>- 회사 정보</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7ffb780e-4322-4673-928a-924556dfde5c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 템플릿에 등록된 기본 정보를 수정할 수 있습니다. 이 부분은 고객에게서 자료를 받습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ba543a98-0e21-4a11-a477-0da2885bd179\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2f3422b8-fbfd-4dea-a2e2-6b9d0ed1267d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-88cf78e6-d987-42b8-8ac6-05f95badee61\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>- 개인 정보</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-55ee1c64-7b1f-4a41-937f-49e24774e6c9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 이름이나 핸드폰 정보를 받습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5fc453ea-dea9-4393-a5b2-0a6b78dd4bbc\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d9044781-6984-4e37-b47f-ff6c03986e6a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6c755d86-3e0d-4326-b993-2413b3596ce8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>- 기타 요청사항</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-82d3033d-2f16-4bba-b1fe-0cb8ad36aaf6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 요청하는 사항을 텍스트나 사진을 찍어 전송해 디자인 작업시 별도로 요청할 수 있습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c8681ed-2fda-455d-a901-c4da644977ef\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d777a09b-f92d-47bb-b58b-538fb3d542ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-184194d1-e1e3-4b3f-ba9c-75f3110183c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d43d3bd1-5ee8-4615-8346-64257ba8879e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-39e253af-3936-488f-b2fb-a47c00fee489\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>STEP4. 주문서를 통해 받은 정보를 정리하는 페이지가 다음 프로세스입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4c0a9bb3-6c17-4fa3-8d5a-4318268acb43\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c06d1d07-3687-4d8c-afb2-0a26c0d8031e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-db36a376-230f-49d8-8781-5384fa78053d\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">주문서 작성을 통해 받은 정보를 정리하고 커뮤니케이션하는 페이지가 주문서 요청 페이지입니다. 주문서 작성이 끝나면 관리자페이지와 연동하여 고객으로 받은 정보를 검토하여 견적서를 보내드릴 수 있어야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aa9c1d7d-165a-453e-9606-66449cd00076\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5a7d9955-6eea-4ae5-afb0-7961eb61388b\" style=\"color:#777777;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dcca41cb-e4d8-4d42-9653-f4b1c7ff73f8\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5d320e2b-7231-42fe-9c9a-0f4a6d63c936\" style=\"color:#777777;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-86fca81f-b222-40e5-8e92-4848ee243cfa\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e07cd91-37af-444d-8736-7cde972613a1\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음회는 다른 예시로 주문단 마무리하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a9351cda-aa41-4740-9a9a-a49f05f4ebf5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:686px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222888436979/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d6ab1141-543e-471e-b378-e8c33ac60833\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5eaa10f8-c99f-4641-bfc9-8ff700b3397a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5ea81e6f-d35b-403e-b93b-b35706e10114\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-7958457d-a943-416a-887a-b946b17fee96\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5eec9fad-e6c1-4666-b2b8-c84ad77979e1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-359e95f1-bab5-4228-83f8-a0c68240eb49\" style=\"\">다음 글의 내용입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-081715ef-600d-4838-9ac3-70ad2e884c2a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1031e96c-bc2d-4e75-9224-e4b3f4e62ebf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f0708743-70bf-470a-a375-a13b2731ea5b\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-19827b41-c435-4b95-b9e8-22f87cd381fd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2c5b9a99-d157-40b1-9c23-cf7a0e23f21c\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb8b93f2-e281-4d5f-9c4b-6ee9ee082678\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a73a2ffa-eb66-4d30-b938-38cadcb0a14d\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-43d3add0-5913-4c5e-8147-d96786d7a302\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-47d91586-918b-4221-8706-546c278ea9a2\" style=\"\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ccb74d80-0ef5-4195-9ed1-c11a11dc2dae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222888436979/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-510d2506-3708-4f94-865a-aab0390deb3c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e041f364-8127-49c3-b9d5-8b69d546c1ea\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a87078b7-d076-41db-a43f-1c89158b7af2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
